reviews.headline: Good lip product
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] Application is typical slanted application for easy application. I like how it's thinner and elongated. The scent is minimal and the shade is very cute and almost natural! I love the design of the product, cute and sweet.

reviews.headline: Plush, non-sticky shine with a perfect plumping finish.
reviews.comments: This gloss gives a stunning plumping effect without the sting. The formula is smooth and cushiony, with a juicy finish that makes lips look fuller instantly. It's not sticky at all, which is rare for glosses! The scent is soft and pleasant, and the packaging feels modern and cute. I love the natural tint it gives, and how hydrating it feels. If you want high shine with volume and comfort ‚Äî this is a must-try.

reviews.headline: Glossy With a Touch of Color
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I was surprised but happy to receive Lychee in this gloss.  I had never heard of the brand before, but so far so good!  I love this gloss!  It's sheer with a hint of soft, non-sticky color.  Plus for the price point (I hoard so many glosses), I can't argue with buying more.

reviews.headline: Glassy look
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I love how shiny this is. This lipgloss is the perfect balance of moisture and shine. It isn't too watery so it actually lasts. It smells great and gives the glass lip effect. I did struggle a bit to open the tube but I have a hand disability.

reviews.headline: Shine Without the Stickiness
reviews.comments:
*Please note I received this product for free in exchange for my honest review. 

This gloss in Vanilla 70% gives a neutral nude to a light pinky look. It's a gorgeous color that has nice pigment with a beautiful glossy shine that gives juicy vibes from back in the day. It is the perfect addition for a "clean girl" makeup look. 

The doe-foot applicator makes it feel fun and easy to swipe on, and the gel texture is smooth and cushiony without feeling sticky (HUGE plus!). I didn't notice any strong scent, just a lightly sweet, pleasant aroma, but it was hardly noticeable. 

It layers nicely over anything and keeps lips looking hydrated and effortlessly glossy all day.  I'm glad I've found this brand as this gloss has made me a huge fan!

reviews.headline: Dear fwee, did you make this just for me?!
reviews.comments: I received this product in exchange for my honest review.Great gloss! Glam volume! This is my first time trying a fwee brand lip gloss and I am so glad I did! The color is lychee and in my opinion it looks good with my skin tone. The pigment really pops and a little goes a long way. The gloss stays shiny for a long time. I experienced an instant plumping and major hydration thanks to the added Vitamin E. Personally, I love the lip applicator and its shape it makes it easy to apply. I will definitely check out more shades, love it!

reviews.headline: Love this lippie
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This is my first experience with Fwee but I got a tell you, I'm sold. This lippie is not sticky and has high shine gloss that lasts. The first time I wore it in public, the girl who took my order at the coffee shop asked me where I got it because it was so pretty! Love, love, love it!

reviews.headline: Game changing gloss!
reviews.comments:
[I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I've been absolutely loving the Fwee 3D Volumizing Gloss! The formula is lightweight yet super glossy, giving my lips that plump, fuller look without feeling sticky. It glides on effortlessly, adds the perfect shine, and makes my lips feel instantly hydrated and smooth.  I love how easy it was to apply outside and enhance my look effortlessly. 

The ingredients are natural and hydrating.  I'm very impressed with the subtle smell and look.  I would absolutely recommend this lip gloss to anyone!

reviews.headline: Love this
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I've been using the fwee 3D Voluming Gloss 70%, and I honestly love how it makes my lips look. The texture is thick and cushiony but not sticky, so it feels really comfortable to wear, and the glossy shine instantly makes my lips look fuller. The sweet scent is fun without being overpowering, and I actually catch myself reapplying just because I enjoy it. The packaging is sleek and easy to throw in my bag, and the applicator makes it quick to put on when I'm on the go. At around $17, it's not the cheapest gloss out there, but with how plump and hydrated it makes my lips look, I feel like it's totally worth it.

reviews.headline: Not sticky
reviews.comments: This gloss is such a pretty everyday staple. The shade B01 Vanilla gives my lips that soft, milky-beige wash that looks so fresh and natural, almost like a perfect "your lips but better" nude. What makes it special is the 3D voluming effect it instantly makes my lips look fuller and smoother without feeling sticky or heavy. The formula is lightweight, cushiony, and has that glassy shine that just catches the light beautifully. I love that it layers well on its own or over lip liner and lipstick, giving me that plumped-up, juicy finish every time. It's one of those glosses that feels comfortable enough to wear all day, and the color is so versatile it pairs with any makeup look

reviews.headline: Perfect Gloss
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I absolutely adore the lip gloss. The shape of the bottle is very unique just like the product. It leaves my lips feeling hydrated and looking like 1 million bucks definitely lives on making them look more voluptuous. Has a great scent and taste too.

reviews.headline: pigmented for sure
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This gloss is definitely voluminous and shiny on the lips. It's highly pigmented and definitely lives up to its claims. My only complaint is that is feels a little heavy on the lips once it's applied and the packaging is cute, but clunky. But overall the product works well and I definitely recommend!

reviews.headline: I'm buying this again and again!
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I loveeeee this!! i have been wearing this everyday! Its not too heavyweight more light but the finish is amazing. It plumps up your lips. The packaging is super cute and fits perfectly in your purse. It's definitely worth the buy. Can't wait to try the other colors.

reviews.headline: So Fun!!
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This is such a fun gloss! The box that it comes in is a little odd because the font and design makes it a little cheap, but the packaging of the product itself makes up for it. It has an iridescent and futuristic design that makes it unlike any product I've seen recently. The gloss smells fruity and the color Lychee is so pretty. It's a little stickier than I'd like a gloss to be, but it's very pretty on the lips and the slight stain it leaves is great. Not a huge fan of the applicator because I think a doe foot shape is best. Overall, very happy with this product and would recommend!

reviews.headline: Great lip gloss
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This lip gloss bottle is very cute shape and nice little bottle. Color is really pretty. I like it with my skin tone. Has a slight scent that smells pretty.

reviews.headline: Great 3D lip gloss
reviews.comments:
This lip gloss has absolutely stunning and very sleek looking design. It's. Wry nice even just to hold it in my hand. 
I absolutely love how this 3D voluming gloss makes my lips look juicy, plump, and hydrated with a syrupy glaze that glides on smoothly (watch the video - you will see what I am talking about). I definitely can see how my lips look more plumped when wearing this 3D lip gloss.  Another thing I love about -  is that it feels non-sticky on my lips. It has very nice sweet scent but absolutely not strong which o appreciate.
Overall I can say that this 3D lip gloss with a bit of color is perfect "go to" for everyday and any occasion!

You're left with the perfect pink gloss in your lips that will compliment any look. The packaging is also really fun as it's small enough to fit in any purse!

faceoff_positive.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This is such a great lip gloss! First of all, the packaging for this gloss is super adorable! It has some curves to it and I love how long and pointy the applicator is. This makes it perfect for getting into the corners of your lips as well as making the cupids bow look nice and sharp. It is super smooth feeling on the lips as well. Although it's a thick gloss and you can definitely tell it's there, it is not sticky at all which I love about it. There's not much of a scent but whatever it is is pleasant. It makes my lips feel super moisturized and doesn't have any plumping stinging effects if you are not into that. It makes your lips look super hydrated and I love the nice color that it gives them. It seems like there's not a ton of product for the price, but a little goes a long way so keep that in mind. I highly recommend! Thank you again for sending it to me!
faceoff_positive.headline: Super smooth!

faceoff_negative.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I like the look of this lip gloss, but that is all it was, just gloss. It did not give any 3D volumizing affect after using it. It was not sticky and sat well on my lips. It did not have a smell to it either.
